FT  13 SEP 94 / People: Non-executive directors
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Sir Paul Girolami, who steps down as chairman of Glaxo in a couple of
months' time, has picked up another retirement job. He is joining the board
of Saatchi &amp; Saatchi as a non-executive director on October 3. He joined the
