<HEADLINE>
FT  12 SEP 94 / World Bond Markets: US Treasury Bond Futures (CBT) Dollars
100,000 32nds of 100%
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
        Open  Sett price   Change   High    Low   Est. vol.  Open int.
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Sep   102-10      100-22    -1-20 102-14  100-17      8,397   124,434
Dec   101-14       99-25    -1-21 101-19   99-20    215,223   312,632
Mar   100-29       99-03    -1-20 100-29   98-30        830     7,647
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
